verbose_text: In metabolic pathway of valine, first, valine changes to methylacrylyl CoA in three stages; then, methylacrylyl CoA changes to 3-hydroxyisobutyryl-CoA by crotonase, and in the next step, 3-hydroxyisobutyryl-CoA changes to 3-hydroxyisovaleric acid by HIBCH and after one other step, it turns to the end product propionyl CoA finally 4.
